  <description><![CDATA[<h2>Walk through Italy's most striking mountain ranges this summer on an outdoor-lover's holiday. From the Dolomites to the South Tyrol, this is the perfect multi-centre for exploring Northern Italy. </h2>
<p>Choose between a multi-centre holiday to <a data-udi="umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7" href="/{localLink:umb://document/c5c478381e04431da3f69d8364215ae7}" title="Merano">Merano</a> &amp; <a data-udi="umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/4c9fc09241f14e3c80acb89b5c9226dd}" title="Selva">Selva</a>, or Selva &amp; <a data-udi="umb://document/7075240655bf40a19a9c77b24d8c5082" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7075240655bf40a19a9c77b24d8c5082}" title="Canazei">Canazei</a>, three of our most popular resorts in and around the <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/italy/the-dolomites" title="The Dolomites">Dolomites</a>. The Italian mountains are so diverse, each town with its own micro-culture and dialect, so it's worth getting to know each area on your summer holiday and scoping out your favourite one!</p>
<h3>Guide price from: £1,681pp*</h3>
<h3>Your multi-centre holiday options:</h3>
<ul>
<li>7, 10, 11 or 14 nights accommodation in your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Travel on Wednesday or Saturday</li>
</ul>
<h3>Your holiday includes:</h3>
<ul>
<li>Return flights from the UK</li>
<li>Return airport transfers to and from your chosen hotels</li>
<li>Taxi transfers between your chosen destinations</li>
<li>Up to two included guided walks per person per week when staying in Selva, Merano, Canazei</li>
</ul>
