  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Walk through Italy's most striking mountain ranges this summer on an outdoor-lover's multi-centre holiday. From the Dolomites to the South Tyrol there's so much to discover in Italy's mountains, from tasting traditional delicacies, listening to local dialects and walking through natural parks. There's nothing quite like exploring the mountains on your summer holiday.</p>]]></listingDescription>
